      "description": "Discontinuing mobile support: The mobile experience does not meet quality standards. A dedicated text-to-speech app is recommended for mobile use.\r\n\r\nAudio files can still be generated on desktop via the Obsidian note reader plugin and synchronized to a mobile device for playback in any audiobook or media player. The desktop version supports exporting audio for a single note or an entire folder of notes in one operation.",
