      "author": "mudnug",
      "description": "- **Smart Highlight Recovery** — If you edit your notes mid-playback, highlighting now adjusts to stay in sync, as long as edit are above the area being read.\r\n- **Pause & Resume with Position Memory** — Pausing now visually shows exactly where you left off.\r\n- **Resume Reading Position** — The plugin remembers your last spot even after closing Obsidian. (optional)\r\n- **Choose Audio File Location** — New options to control where generated audio is saved.\r\n- **More Voices + Filtering** — Added more voices and a language/region filter.\r\n- **Theme Gallery** — Preview all highlight themes in a gallery view.\r\n",
