      "description": "- **Cancel audio generation anytime** – You can now stop audio generation mid-process if you change your mind by closing the tab\r\n- **Cleaner look** – Same familiar appearance, now using Obsidian's official SettingGroup API for better consistency with the rest of Obsidian\r\n- **Online TTS no longer available on mobile** – The online voice provider has made changes that prevent mobile support. Mobile users can still use local voices installed on their device.",
